{"tid":1427193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[機埸員工] 真心唔好衝禁區","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:26:02.000Z","uid":24574,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"674bdf897306dfe4dfb0f41d4535985291176c0f","tid":1427193,"uid":24574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"每個入得禁區既位都係大量 AVSECO (機埸保安) 守住, 就算衝過佢地個關之後仲有入境D閘頂住<br />\n<br />\n再加上入左去之後唔會有野做到, 唔係機埸做既人跟本唔會熟路<br />\n<br />\n要入境既人一定要經接機大堂 (5/F), 要出境既都一定要經出境大堂 (Departure hall 6/F)<br />\n<br />\n所以絕對冇原因要入禁區, 唔好做冇結果既野, 送頭, 送新聞俾狗仔報"},{"pid":"df992df712c179ffe6af6cabd1726c662974e55f","tid":1427193,"uid":24574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:25:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b5e60f5d885ca70024581e46630c6448a6f4f8e","tid":1427193,"uid":148960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:26:02.000Z","msg":"[綜合討論] 目前運動出現嘅問題以至未來方向<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dydHsS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dydHsS</a><br />\n幫幫手推下"}]}